ATHLETE OF THE WEEK: GIRLS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Amy Skieresz 
</P>
<P>
 SCHOOL: Agoura 
</P>
<P>
 SPORT: Cross-country 
</P>
<P>
 YEAR: Senior 
</P>
<P>
 SEASON AT A GLANCE: Skieresz has won 12 of 13 races, including six in a row 
since finishing third in the individual sweepstakes race of the Mt.San Antonio 
College Invitational on Oct. 22. Included in that streak are her third 
consecutive victories in the Ventura County, Marmonte League and Southern 
Section championships. 
</P>
