CHOOSING A PRIVATE SCHOOL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The San Fernando Valley is home to more than 200 private schools, where one of 
every five Valley students attends classes. Today, The Times profiles the 
largest of those schools. B5 
