 The incident occurred as Manhattan jurors began deliberations in Shakur's 
trial. He and his road manager, Charles Fuller, 23, are charged with forcibly 
sodomizing and sexually abusing a woman in Shakur's New York hotel suite Nov. 
18, 1993. 
</P>
<P>
 Defense lawyers said the rapper denied forcing the woman to have sex, and that 
she brought charges after seeing him with another woman. 
