 Chattaway, Norman James, 63, of Simi Valley, retired draftsman for McDonnell 
Douglas.Pierce Brothers Griffin Mortuary, Thousand Oaks. 
</P>
<P>
 Cox, Hermoyne Potter, 91, of Thousand Oaks, homemaker. Pierce Bothers Griffin 
Mortuary, Thousand Oaks. 
</P>
<P>
 Hamblin, Edward, 61, of Oxnard, recreational vehicle mechanic at Granny's 
Campers. Ted Mayr Funeral Home, Ventura. 
</P>
<P>
 Marley, James A. Jr., 64, of Thousand Oaks, retired salesman for Karastan Rug 
Mills. Pierce Brothers Griffin Mortuary, Thousand Oaks. 
</P>
<P>
 Parry, Esther Whitlock, 90, of Ventura, homemaker. Ted Mayr Funeral Home, 
Ventura. 
</P>
<P>
 Turner, Alice Bernice, 89, of Ventura, homemaker. Charles Carroll Funeral 
Home, Ventura. 
</P>
