 Other top-10 caliber teams include Newport Harbor opening the Fullerton 
tournament against Whittier La Serna at 5:30 p.m., and Troy playing the 7:30 
p.m. game against Santa Ana Valley in the Century tournament. 
</P>
<P>
 The Irvine tournament also opens with the host team playing Anaheim at 7:45 
p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 The University and Woodbridge tournaments get under way on Saturday. MARTIN 
HENDERSON 
