<P>
 SAN CLEMENTE 03,17,09,08 1993-94 RECORDS OVERALL LEAGUE 12-12 3-7 02,10,18 
COACH RECORD AT SCHOOL Ed Coyle 12-12 04,20,05,06,04 RETURNING STARTERS YR. 
HGT. P Paul Anderson Sr. 6-1 G Mike Castaneda Sr. 6-0 G 04,15,05,06,04 TOP 
