<TEXT>
<P>
 MATER DEI 03,17,09,08 1993-94 RECORDS OVERALL LEAGUE 34-1 10-0 02,15,18 COACH 
RECORD AT SCHOOL Gary McKnight 352-29 04,20,05,09,04 RETURNING STARTERS YR. 
