<P>
 CAPISTRANO VALLEY 03,17,09,08 1993-94 RECORDS OVERALL LEAGUE 15-11 4-6 
02,15,18 COACH RECORD AT SCHOOL Mark Thornton 292-83 04,20,05,06,04 RETURNING 
STARTERS YR. HGT. P John Earnest Sr. 6-7 C 04,17,05,06,05 TOP RETURNERS YR. 
HGT. P Peter D'Aquanni Sr. 6-6 F Todd Hector Jr. 6-3 G/F Randy Shepard Jr. 6-2 
