<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFCASE: AUTOMOTIVE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Compiled John O'Dell / Times Staff WriterSouth Coast Repertory Theater Pays 
Tribute to Mazda Motor's Chief 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 South Coast Repertory and the Japan Business Assn. are hosting a tribute to 
Mazda Motor of America President Kazuo (Sonny) Sonoguci on Dec. 13 in 
recognition of the Irvine-based company's philanthropy, including its 
longstanding financial support of the Costa Mesa theater group. 
</P>
